      <title>马克龙看守政府正在为长期执政做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙正在为在未来数月内以权力有限的看守政府来管理法国做准备，因为他将把法国推向未知的宪法领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统发表重要经济讲话前维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-to-hold-rates-before-president-s-key-economy-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年以来，经济学家们首次对南非央行是否继续维持 2009 年高位利率或是否放松利率产生了分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-africa-to-hold-rates-before-president-s-key-economy-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在电视采访中表示，如果健康状况恶化，哈里斯可能领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-says-harris-could-take-over-second-term-if-health-changed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对有关其任职能力的持续质疑，总统乔·拜登表示，如果他赢得第二任期但由于健康原因无法完成任期，他愿意将权力移交给副总统卡马拉·哈里斯——但他不认为出现这种情况的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/biden-says-harris-could-take-over-second-term-if-health-changed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 03:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
